title: Trump Hikes Global Tariffs From 10% To 15% Day After Big Supreme Court Order
summary_full: US President Donald Trump on Saturday raised the global tariffs from 10 per cent to 15 per cent after a big setback in Supreme Court on Friday.
summary_public: US President Donald Trump on Saturday raised the global tariffs from 10 per cent to 15 per cent after a big setback in Supreme Court on Friday.
